#### Description

This dashboard provides visibility into node distribution within the Nozomi Networks platform using the Node data stream.

It includes metrics for total, public, and private nodes, with visualizations by OS, type, vendor, zone, and role. The dashboard highlights the top node protocols and VLAN IDs. A saved search displays essential node details to support asset tracking and analysis.
